        <updateDate>2016-02-18T15:46:20Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Youth Exchange Support Act of 2015</strong></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to increase from $50 to $400 per month the amount of the charitable contribution tax deduction for taxpayers who provide housing and support to a student enrolled in an educational program. This increased amount is adjusted for inflation for taxable years beginning after 2016. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
